window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Alex Baudelaire has finally played his hand… And it’s a doozy.</p> <p>The earth’s oldest and darkest magic has been stirred, and from it the berserkers have risen once more. The last time they walked the earth, it trembled under their weight and the blood that flowed from their rampage nearly drowned the world. Alex has offered Doc a choice: Doc's life in exchange for the world. But even if Doc sacrifices himself, will that actually be enough to sate the blood lust of the berserkers? Has Doc finally met an opponent he can't beat? Dive into a hidden world of magic and mayhem to find out now! Listen this eighteenth book in the legendary ongoing series today! (Do it now... You know you want to.)</p> <p>Also Click 'Follow' Beside the Author Name So You Don't Miss Release Updates!</p> <p>So, what are you waiting for... Get the book already! And always remember: W.W.D.D. What-Would-Doc-Do? (He'd tip a glass, kick some ass, and then enjoy this great new book. And you should too!) Happy Listening!</p> <p>And get your FREE Doc eBook at mmcrumley.com</p> <p>THE IMMORTAL DOC HOLLIDAY On-going Series Titles</p> <p>Book 1: HIDDEN...</p> <p>Book 13: HELLION</p> <p>Book 14: SHADOWS</p> <p>Book 15: INDEBTED</p> <p>Book 16: FATHOM</p> <p>Book 17: FEROCITY</p> <p>Book 18: ONSLAUGHT</p> <p>Book 19: ECHOES</p> <p>&amp; More Coming Soon...</p>"; 
